      <h1 class='title'>Abattoirs</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 cc1659-60WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_1659ws' title='Col. 1659WS &mdash; HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1659WS' name='column_1659ws' href='#column_1659ws' rel='bookmark'>1659WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_61'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-james-gray' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_61' title='Link to this speech by Mr James Gray' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-james-gray" title="Mr James Gray">Mr. Gray</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">To ask the Secretary of State for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs how many abattoirs in the UK are licensed to kill over 30 month old cattle. [188491]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_62'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-alun-michael' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_62' title='Link to this speech by Mr Alun Michael' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-alun-michael" title="Mr Alun Michael">Alun Michael</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">There are currently 20 abattoirs in the UK contracted to slaughter cattle for the over 30 months scheme.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_63'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-james-gray' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_63' title='Link to this speech by Mr James Gray' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-james-gray" title="Mr James Gray">Mr. Gray</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">To ask the Secretary of State for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs whether cattle over 30 months may be transported to slaughter in the same lorry as those under 30 months. [188494]</p><a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_1660ws' title='Col. 1660WS &mdash; HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1660WS' name='column_1660ws' href='#column_1660ws' rel='bookmark'>1660WS</a>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_64'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-alun-michael' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_64' title='Link to this speech by Mr Alun Michael' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-alun-michael" title="Mr Alun Michael">Alun Michael</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">Cattle over 30 months can be transported to slaughter in the same lorry as those under 30 months, providing that all necessary animal movement and welfare legislation is adhered to.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
